701178f-a.title: Bronx: Grand Concourse - 188th Street (East)
701178f-a.text:
Grand Concourse, west side, north from E. 188th Street, showing the thoroughfare passing underneath the E. Fordham Road bridge. The W.P.A. sign indicates that a highway project is to be started
here.
1937
W.P.A. Photo
Five Boroughs Project
